name: No More Heroes Style 英雄不再
description:
我感觉接触这游戏的人应该不是很多？ 但是我觉得画风还是不错的。

我使用anythingv4.5和Silicon29，权重0.7-0.9。

lora内含两种画风，可以使用2D或者3D来切换画风。

I feel that not many people should be exposed to this game? But I think the drawing style is still good.

I use anythingv4.5 and Silicon29 with a weight of 0.7-0.9.

lora contains two painting styles, you can use 2D or 3D to switch the painting style.
